datasets.name: dataset_5
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', Event_Date_Time) AS Monthly_Event_Date, Screen AS Screen, SUM(Unique_Screen_Views) AS Total_Unique_Screen_Views FROM hpx_events_model WHERE Event_Date_Time >= '2023-05-01' AND Screen NOT IN ('home', 'welcome', 'welcomecontainer', 'welcome-core', 'support') AND Ui_Action = 'screendisplayed' AND Screen IN (SELECT Screen FROM hpx_events_model GROUP BY Screen ORDER BY SUM(Unique_Screen_Views) DESC LIMIT 10) GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', Event_Date_Time), Screen ORDER BY Monthly_Event_Date

frame.title: Top Unique Screen Views Over Time
